<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>[subscriber:firstname | default:Subscriber],</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You recently joined our list and we\'d like to give you a warm welcome!</p>'=>'<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>مرحبًا، أيها المشترك الجديد</strong></h1>
